foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although VA indicated in its FY 2010 Annual Report that there were 1,385 requests pending at the end of the fiscal year, the figure denoted in this chart is correct. The difference is attributed to the following: 1) in some instances the office did not show requests that were in fact completed in FY 2010 as completed in VA’s FOIA tracking system until after the FY 2010 report was finalized, and 2) there were some discrepancies in accounting.
